    </p><p><b>By Helicopter</b><br />Pawan Hans Helicopter Service Is Available Between Guwahati Airport And Shillong Helipad.   
    
    <p><b>Travelling By Train</b><br />
    There Are No Railway Lines In Meghalaya. Guwahati Is The Nearest Railway Station Located Around 104Kms. From Shillong.
    <p><b>Travelling By Road</b><br />
        Shillong Is Connected With Guwahati By NH 40. Various Modes Of Transport Including Shared Taxis, Buses And Private Cabs Ply On This Route. The Road Is Damaged By Landslide, It Will Take 2.50 Hours In An Automobile.
